title: Oasis - Almost Full Discography [FLAC]
description:
I added the Apple Lossless discography to Pirate Bay, and most people wanted it in .FLAC, so finally, here it is.   Includes the new album, Dig Out Your Soul, as well as the bonus disc to that. 

If someone could add the b-sides to the "Don&#039;t Believe The Truth" singles, that would be GREAT! I have a few but not all of them.   That&#039;s why it&#039;s not a true discography of Oasis.   Most is contained here!

Enjoy!
